text: The Liberia women's national under-18 and under-19 basketball team is a national basketball team of Liberia, administered by the Liberia Basketball Federation.Profile - Liberia, FIBA.com, Retrieved 2 June 2016. It represents the country in international under-18 and under-19 (under age 19 and under age 18) women's basketball competitions. It appeared at the 2010 FIBA Africa Under-18 Championship for Women qualification stage. ==See also== *Liberia women's national basketball team *Liberia women's national under-17 basketball team *Liberia men's national under-19 basketball team ==References== ==External links== *Archived records of Liberia team participations Category:Basketball in Liberia Category:Basketball teams in Liberia Category:Women's national under-19 basketball teams Basketball
